des:
Comedies of vaigai puyal Vadivelu in tamil. Just say 'start comedies of vadivelu' to get into skill. Once you are inside, say 'play' or 'start' to continue. 'More' or 'Next' for the next clips, 'Repeat' of hear it again. 'Stop' or 'Cencel' to end skill. It is that Simple.

Have fun with vadivelu comedy. Don't forget to rate it if you like it.
